title: No Evidence of Collusion | Guests: Gov. Scott Walker & Tim Pool | 5/14/20
description:
When did we go from “flatten the curve” to “don’t leave your house until the virus disappears"? Michigan barber Karl Manke had his license suspended for keeping his shop open. Former Wisconsin Gov. Scott Walker joins after his state’s supreme court overturned the stay-at-home order. Journalist Tim Pool calls out the media for ignoring Obamagate in the face of overwhelming evidence. The list of Flynn unmaskers is not about politics – it’s about YOU. Port of Seattle police officer Greg Anderson joins to explain why he spoke out in a viral video against arresting lockdown violators. Glenn breaks down exactly what Obamagate is and how officials admitted they NEVER had evidence of Russian collusion.
